## Advanced Usage

### Scripting:
You can use scripting in "BudgetBuddy" to automate financial tasks. Example script to automatically generate monthly reports:
```python
import budgetbuddy

budget = budgetbuddy.load('October')
report = budget.generate_report()
budgetbuddy.send_report(report, 'email@example.com')
```

